Interface ProductVariantImport

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ImportResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProductVariantImportImpl

    public interface ProductVariantImport
extends ImportResource

    Import representation for a product variant. Use this type for importing new product variants into a commercetools project.
